  <%= image_tag 'icon_logo/text_img_discover_105x142.png' %><br/>
  Find places near you,<br/>
  wherever you are.
</div>
<div class="border_hack"></div>
<div id="mobile_head">
  <%= image_tag 'icon_logo/text_img_mobile_84x142.png' %><br/>
  Phone &amp; feet are all that<br/>
  are needed to Amble.<br/>
  <p class='sub'>
    We support most mobile<br/>
      browsers and PCSs
  </p>
